title: [Brrr Necessities]
description: Brightly lit oil lamps reflect off an ironwood-trimmed full-length mirror situated near one of the tables.  Elsewhere, makeup-dusted display trays flank the tent's cloth walls.  Inkpots and jars are gathered on a central worktable next to flower petals and multicolored, ground herbs where a young assistant apothecary combines the ingredients in a large bowl.
